README.md

Awesome

   Everyone loves a bit of BEM in their development. Here's just the
   starts of hopefully a large list of resources.

Articles

     * [https://assist-software.net/blog/css-guideline-tutorial-bem-sass]A
       CSS Guideline Tutorial: BEM with Sass
     * [https://medium.com/@stowball/bemantic-dry-like-you-mean-it-133ea38
       43d98#.a2ivj7ny9]BEMantic - DRY like you mean it
     * [https://www.lullabot.com/articles/bem-atomic-design-a-css-architec
       ture-worth-loving]BEM & Atomic Design: A CSS Architecture Worth
       Loving
     * [https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2016/06/battling-bem-extended-edi
       tion-common-problems-and-how-to-avoid-them/]Battling BEM (Extended
       Edition): 10 Common Problems And How To Avoid Them
     * [http://www.sitepoint.com/bem-smacss-advice-from-developers/]BEM
       and SMACSS: Advice From Developers Who've Been There
     * [http://csswizardry.com/2013/01/mindbemding-getting-your-head-round
       -bem-syntax/]MindBEMding - getting your head 'round BEM syntax -
       CSS Wizardry
     * [https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2012/04/a-new-front-end-methodolo
       gy-bem/]A New Front-End Methodology: BEM - Smashing Magazine
     * [https://www.smashingmagazine.com/a-new-front-end-methodology-bem-b
       locks-reiteration/]A New Front-End Methodology: BEM (Blocks
       Reiteration) - Smashing Magazine
     * [https://www.smashingmagazine.com/front-end-methodology-bem-file-sy
       stem-representation/]A New Front-End Methodology: BEM (File System
       Representation For A Block) - Smashing Magazine
     * [https://css-tricks.com/bem-101/]BEM 101 - CSS Tricks
     * [http://webdesign.tutsplus.com/articles/an-introduction-to-the-bem-
       methodology--cms-19403]An Introduction to the BEM Methodology -
       Tuts Plus
     * [https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2014/07/bem-methodology-for-small
       -projects/]Scaling Down The BEM Methodology For Small Projects -
       Smashing Magazine
     * [http://www.integralist.co.uk/posts/bem.html]Maintainable CSS with
       BEM - Integralist
     * [http://blog.kaelig.fr/post/48196348743/fifty-shades-of-bem]Fifty
       Shades of BEM - Kaelig
     * [https://robots.thoughtbot.com/keeping-the-frontend-modular-with-be
       m]Keeping the Front-End Modular with BEM - Thoughtbot
     * [http://philbaker.me/2014/02/css-class-naming-and-bem-contemporary-
       practice/]CSS class naming and BEM: Contemporary practice - Phil
       Baker
