       Naming conventions - BEM - Shane Prendergast
     * [https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2013/02/the-history-of-the-bem-me
       thodology/]The Evolution Of The BEM Methodology - Smashing Magazine
     * [http://blog.8thlight.com/nelsol-batalla/2014/08/01/bem-basics.html
       ]BEM Basics - 8th Light
     * [https://medium.com/@Codebryo/how-to-bem-4a55fa3cd429]How To BEM -
       Roman Kuba
     * [http://codepen.io/andersschmidt/post/expressive-bem-with-sass-a-di
       fferent-approach]Expressive BEM with Sass: a different approach -
       Anders Hansen
     * [http://codepen.io/andersschmidt/post/expressive-bem-with-sass-part
       -ii-a-first-draft-of-mixins]Expressive BEM with Sass Part II: A
       first draft of mixins - Anders Hansen
     * [http://mono.company/journal/frontend/learning-to-love-bem//]Learni
       ng to love BEM
     * [http://www.sitepoint.com/working-bem-scale-advice-top-developers/]
       Working with BEM at Scale -- Advice From Top Developers
     * [https://medium.com/@mjtweaver/css-architecture-bemcss-block-elemen
       t-modifier-e642bd0f4218]CSS Architecture: BEMCSS--Block, Element &
