     * [http://www.joelambert.co.uk/article/bem-guidelines/]BEM Guidelines
       for component focused development
     * [http://csswizardry.com/2015/08/bemit-taking-the-bem-naming-convent
       ion-a-step-further/]BEMIT: Taking the BEM Naming Convention a Step
