       Methodologies Part 3
     * [http://www.theodo.fr/blog/2015/10/how-i-stopped-worrying-and-learn
       ed-to-love-the-css-with-bem/]How I stopped worrying and learned to
       love the CSS with BEM
     * [https://ahmadawais.com/bem-css-basics-for-wordpress-themes-develop
       ers/]BEM CSS Basics for WordPress Themes Developers
     * [http://codepen.io/craigmdennis/post/generate-responsive-bemit-clas
       ses-with-sass]Generate responsive BEMIT classes with Sass
     * [http://www.jamesturneronline.net/beautifulweb/bemit-naming-convent
       ion.html]The BEMIT naming convention
     * [http://4digits.net/blog/sass/introduction-to-bem.html]An
       Introduction to the BEM Methodology for effective Front-End
       Development
     * [http://www.blankmaker.com/css-organization-with-bem/]CSS
       Organisation with BEM
     * [https://dominikpiatek.com/patterns-for-scaling-css/]Patterns For
       Scaling CSS
     * [https://m.alphasights.com/our-new-flatmate-bem-15591204af04#.paldm
       aoyp]Our New Flatmate BEM
     * [https://seesparkbox.com/foundry/bem_by_example]BEM by example
     * [https://assortment.io/posts/introducing-bem-css-naming-convention]
